### Organic Search Traffic Share

- Organic search drives **53.3%** of all website traffic across industries (BrightEdge)
- Paid search accounts for **15%** of website traffic (BrightEdge)
- Social media drives **5%** of website traffic (BrightEdge)
- AI referrals account for approximately **1%** of website traffic — but this figure is growing every quarter (BrightEdge/Conductor)

### Platform-Specific User Behaviour

| Behaviour | Google Search | ChatGPT Search | Perplexity |
|---|---|---|---|
| Average session duration | **1–2 minutes** | **8–12 minutes** | **5–8 minutes** |
| Queries per session | **1.5–2** | **5–8** | **3–5** |
